### List All Models with Metadata
### Expected: JSON list of all available deployments with gateway metadata

GET {{host}}/v1/models
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Response Format:
### {
###   "object": "list",
###   "data": [
###     {
###       "id": "gpt-4o",
###       "object": "model",
###       "created": 1700000000,
###       "owned_by": "gpt",
###       "permission": [],
###       "root": "gpt-4o",
###       "parent": null,
###       "gateway": {
###         "deployment_name": "gpt-4o-global",
###         "model_family": "gpt",
###         "protocol_family": "chat-completions",
###         "azure_model_name": "gpt-4o",
###         "endpoint": "...",
###         "fallback": "gpt-4o-mini" | null
###       }
###     }
###   ]
### }
